column5: Pretty cool pic of a sturgeon getting ready to do its thing in the highwaters of rainy river. Pretty good size too id say 5-6ft
Do love those fish.  Gentle giants... except inbetween the hookset and the landing.  Cool shot.
Just throw that hook onto the end of his tail and hold on haha
Yeah the power in these fish is obsurd.  Beautiful creatures
A few more days and there will be 1000's sitting right there?  Then its go pro time!  Lol i got 2 or 3 years of stugeon spawning vids i still need to edit
Great shot!  Looking forward to the GoPro footage.
edit the damn videos  I have been waiting forever to see them  lol very cool fish
